snippet.title: Monster Hunter: Rise - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for the first free title update which arrives in April for a look at the monster reveal. Master all-new weapon abilities and save the village from the impending Rampage.

Take on Magnamalo when the Monster Hunter Rise demo gets an update on March 11, 2021.

Monster Hunter Rise launches on March 26, 2021 for Nintendo Switch.

#IGN #Gaming
